window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Do you need some help getting to sleep?</p> <p>In this season of <i>Sleep Sound</i>, come with Sienna Miller as she transports you to some of the most relaxing winter and spring scenes on the planet. From a windstorm on an English harbour, to a dawn chorus by an Estonian lake, settle down and snuggle up to the rumble of approaching thunder.</p> <p>Take a deep breath, relax, and join Sienna on an escape to sleep.</p> <p>Now available in Dolby Atmos on Audible.</p>"; 
